T1  - Information, Asset Prices, and the Volume of Trade
AU  - HUFFMAN, GREGORY W.
Y1  - 1992/09/01
PY  - 1992
DA  - 1992/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1992.tb04672.x
